{"type": "article", "id": 29295, "title": "像回旋镖的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-07T23:03:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160707232942hSvBFqabyIKDTYxw.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://www.cardeoli.com/\">Cardeoli</a> 工作室最近参照回旋镖为 <a href=\"http://www.missana.es/en/\">Missana</a> 设计了一套同名的家具系列 <a href=\"http://www.missana.es/en/15-modelos-en/281-boomerang-en\">Boomerang</a>，包括一把长椅和普通的座椅。它们的坐垫和椅背都参照回旋镖采用了圆弧形的设计，椅腿部分则用纤细的黑色和粉色金属框架来代替，带给人一种微妙的平衡感。配合红黑两色的半月形坐垫，看上去简洁优雅，适用于各种环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707233050b4QEgmI6fXLa5OyB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707233050JeDWbRNAZxvSu12m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707233050dNmoKtSnIrMivfgW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}